    <svcproc svcproctype="lubricate" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Breather</title>
        <specpara>
            <caution>
                <para>Cover the breather when steam cleaning the housing to prevent water from entering the housing and
                    contaminating the oil.
                </para>
            </caution>
        </specpara>
        <para>Baffle-type breathers help keep Meritor axles free from external moisture and dirt, which can cause
            premature oil and component failure.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
